{"id":"270585089_Modeling_and_Measuring_Competencies_in_Higher_Education","abstract":"Measuring competencies acquired in higher education has to be regarded as a widely neglected research field. The progress made in empirical research on the school system since the 1990s – for example, through large-scale assessments such as the Trends in International Mathematics and Science Study (TIMSS) and the Programme for International Student Assessment (PISA) and through a massive expansion of instructional research in general – has revealed that nothing comparable exists at the higher education level.","authors":["Sigrid Blömeke","Olga Zlatkin-Troitschanskaia","Christiane Kuhn","Judith Fege"],"meta":["January 2013","In book: Modeling and Measuring Competencies in Higher Education (pp.1-10)Publisher: SensePublishersEditors: Sigrid Blömeke, Olga Zlatkin-Troitschanskaia, Christiane Kuhn, Judith Fege"],"references":["320170077_Lernaufgaben_im_kompetenzorientierten_Geschichtsunterricht","305852595_Higher_Education_and_the_Debate_on_KeyGeneric_Skills","305055873_Bildungsexpansion_und_soziale_Ungleichheit_Zunahme_Abnahme_oder_Persistenz_ungleicher_Chancenverhaltnisse_-_eine_Frage_der_Perspektive","301916981_Assessing_Teaching_and_Assessment_Competences_of_Biology_Teacher_Trainees_Lessons_from_Item_Development","299484994_Student_Growth_from_Service-Learning_A_Comparison_of_First-Generation_and_Non-First-Generation_College_Students","283619174_Leistungstests_zur_Messung_der_professionellen_Kompetenz_fruhpadagogischer_Fachkrafte","281345720_Fachwissen_im_Studium_zum_Lehramt_Physik","281345471_Die_Entwicklung_der_Studienabbruchquoten_an_den_deutschen_Hochschulen_Statistische_Berechnungen_auf_der_Basis_des_Absolventenjahrgangs_2012","281345460_DaWis_Teilprojekt_Fachdidaktisches_Wissen","281345376_Ursachen_des_Studienabbruchs_in_Bachelor-_und_in_herkommlichen_Studiengangen_Ergebnisse_einer_bundesweiten_Befragung_von_Exmatrikulierten_des_Studienjahres_200708","281345365_Modellierung_fac